          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center"><span class="text-gray-400 text-sm font-medium">Line-rate PPS:</span><span id="out-line" class="text-amber-600 font-semibold">1,488,095</span></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center"><span class="text-gray-400 text-sm font-medium">Naive PPS (no overhead):</span><span id="out-naive" class="text-gray-500 font-semibold">1,953,125</span></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center"><span class="text-gray-400 text-sm font-medium">Bandwidth:</span><span id="out-mbps" class="text-teal-600 font-semibold">1,000 Mbps</span></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center"><span class="text-gray-400 text-sm font-medium">On-wire bytes/packet:</span><span id="out-wire" class="text-gray-600 font-semibold">84 B</span></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center"><span class="text-gray-400 text-sm font-medium">Packets per minute:</span><span id="out-ppm" class="text-gray-600 font-semibold">89,285,714</span></div>
