        While researching this page we tested the PPS calculators currently ranking in search — and found that several widely-used ones, including a competing converter site's dedicated PPS tool, <strong>skip Ethernet wire overhead entirely</strong>. They compute <code>rate ÷ (size × 8)</code>, which overstates the packet rate of small-packet traffic by up to <strong>31%</strong>:
